HEADWORD: Autocratrix
<hw>Au*toc"ra*trix</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL.]</ety> <def>A female sovereign who is independent and
absolute; -- a title given to the empresses of Russia.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autocratship</ent>⟦br⟧
